{"tid":1338673,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］朋友喺旺角比人偷咗部手機","createTime":"2019-07-21T14:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:18:12.000Z","uid":279025,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3456b0959fa1123f0b549f486892d222a58e10","tid":1338673,"uid":279025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"我個Friend冇連登Acc 所以佢問我借 向全能嘅連登巴絲求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個friend 3點左右喺旺角地鐵站B2出口附近吾見左電話 疑似比人偷咗 部手機係銀色嘅iPhone XS 有透明殼<br />\n發現嘅時候已經行遠咗 即刻返轉頭 但係都搵唔到<br />\n佢報咗警 但係警察好大機會唔做嘢<br />\n去埋Apple 職員已經幫佢鎖咗部機 但係偷咗個條友唔開機 Find my iPhone都用唔到<br />\n有冇人曾經3點喺旺角B2出口附近見到/執到部手機<br />\n可唔可以比返佢<br />\n佢真係冇哂辦法先想向全能嘅連登巴絲求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望咁多位幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfaf0c22d1270e4f473401a459ec4e30b84d37b","tid":1338673,"uid":9470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"急你老母咩 , 關我撚事"},{"pid":"e93ffc635033653d7670f1ed628abf80b4cc17aa","tid":1338673,"uid":279025,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bfaf0c22d1270e4f473401a459ec4e30b84d37b","tid":1338673,"uid":9470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"急你老母咩 , 關我撚事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"唔洗咁惡嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde87c25e579fc2e86314c633b7d5eb1aa342934","tid":1338673,"uid":122867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三點都唔落灣仔支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉 <br />\n<br />\n算啦 幫推"},{"pid":"b8f5f6df638dd7f09ac23830a29a0d02fec6915b","tid":133867